WEBVTT

00:00.784 --> 00:02.771
Previously on "Manhattan"...

00:02.796 --> 00:07.499
Behold, gentlemen, 150 micrograms

00:07.524 --> 00:09.969
of plutonium-239.

00:10.003 --> 00:13.911
The sample is at Dr. Akley's disposal.

00:14.031 --> 00:16.171
I got keys to the lab. I can let you in.

00:16.327 --> 00:17.367
Really?

00:17.418 --> 00:19.786
What the hell is going on in here?

00:20.288 --> 00:23.623
You conned me into
giving you the plutonium.

00:23.625 --> 00:27.127
I got Frank Winter an outside line today.

00:27.178 --> 00:30.380
He said that you took
work from other scientists

00:30.431 --> 00:31.765
and published it as your own.

00:31.799 --> 00:33.434
That's bullshit, Abby.

00:33.466 --> 00:35.018
They're all whores?

00:35.808 --> 00:39.355
You whiz kids. Always in your heads.

00:39.390 --> 00:41.441
You deserve some fun every once in a while.

00:41.475 --> 00:43.393
As long as you're paid up...

00:49.100 --> 00:52.220
This chrysanthemum, it's
supposed to be white.

00:53.537 --> 00:56.156
My honey bees, they're dead.

00:56.158 --> 00:57.457
All of them.

